snippet.title: Warhammer 40.000: Agents of Death (Sep 10, 2000) [unreleased]
snippet.description:
Warhammer 40.000: Agents of Death is a cancelled FPS, that was in development by Poland's studio Mirage Interactive (mostly known for Imperium Galactica and Mortyr). This game based on an improved engine from Mortyr 2093-1944. This video showed gameplay of the playable beta, which is exclusively multiplayer.
Download: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1rmAGTrmVYTameSn1etdXoMEH4GUotnuq/view
